Detailed Summary of the Sales Analysis Dashboard

1. Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

Total Orders: 1000 orders processed.
Total Revenue: £3,520,984 generated overall.
Average Order-Delivery Time: 5.53 days on average.
Average Customer Spend: £3,520.98 per customer.

2. Revenue Insights

a. Revenue by Occasions
Highest revenue generated from Anniversary, Holi, and Raksha Bandhan occasions.
Lower revenue observed for Birthday and Diwali events.

b. Revenue by Category
Colors and Sweets categories contribute the most to revenue.
Mugs, Plants, and Soft Toys show moderate performance.
Cake category contributes a smaller share.

c. Revenue by Months
Peak revenue in February and August, showing seasonal sales spikes.
Revenue dips observed during April–June and September.

d. Revenue by Location
Ghaziabad, Bhatkal, and Hazratganj are top-earning locations.
Revenue is consistent across locations with no extreme variations.

3. Order Insights

a. Top 10 Cities by Order Volume
Cities like Dhanbad, Imphal, Kavali, and Gunakal show the highest number of orders.
Certain cities maintain moderate but steady order volume.

b. Top 5 Products by Revenue
Best-selling products include Magman Set, Dolores Gift, and Harum Pack.
Deserunt Box and Quia Gift also show strong performance.

4. Dashboard Interactivity
Includes dynamic slicers for:
Delivery Date
Order Date
Occasion
Users can filter the data across months, years, and events for deeper analysis.

5. Overall Analysis Summary
The business shows strong seasonal performance, especially during festive periods.
Certain categories (Colors, Sweets) and cities (Dhanbad, Imphal) significantly drive revenue and orders.
Interactive filters enhance decision-making by allowing customized views of the sales data.
